    <div class="article-body" data-i18n-content="en" style="display:none">
        <p>Web app that calculates a&nbsp;dog's "human" age using the epigenetic formula from UC&nbsp;San Diego researchers. Two input modes: sliders or date of&nbsp;birth. Supports 7&nbsp;languages, installable as&nbsp;PWA.</p>

        <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> Next.js 16, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, Framer Motion, Radix UI, shadcn/ui, next-intl, Serwist (PWA)</p>

